1040 West Harrison Street<br/>
Chicago, IL 60607-7133</p>
<p class="campus_location"><span class="label"><strong>Contact Information: </strong></span><br/>
<span class="campus_location">Campus Location: 3343 ETMSW <br/>
<span class="phone">(312) 996-5650</span> <br/>
<span class="email"><a href="mailto:psphd@uic.edu">psphd@uic.edu</a> </span><br/>
